snippet.title: Popatlal बना School Student | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | 24 Feb 2025
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw7xjxzbMwgBSmbeYwqYRMg

Police finally catches hold of the scammers. Everyone gathers at Bhide's house to inform him that he will get back all his money. Meanwhile, Popatlal tells Tapu and his friends about a celebrity who will be coming to meet them all.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episode No - 587
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Click Here To Watch More Episodes Of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G3QQIKGExbP8b1NqpJKa_xb

snippet.title: HACKER OR WHAT! | JONATHAN IS BACK | BGMI
snippet.description:
Hey Guys, I’m Jonathan Amaral, better known as Jonathan Gaming, a professional BGMI esports athlete and streamer.

Since the start of my journey, my dedication to the game has been defined by precision, consistency, and an unstoppable grind. As an assaulter, I’ve built a reputation for clutch performances and high-impact gameplay, earning respect in the BGMI community. 

Through years of dedication, I’ve honed my skills, adapting to every challenge and evolving with the game. Whether in high-stakes tournaments or streaming for the gaming community, my focus remains the same - pushing the limits and delivering top-tier gameplay.

Official Red Bull Athlete 🪽
MVP of PMCO Fall Split 2019 South Asia 🏅
MVP of PUBG Mobile World League 2020 🌍

snippet.description:
Experience our folksy foot-tapping number " Kollagottinadhiro" from 'Hari Hara Veera Mallu (Telugu)'  🎶🔥 Featuring PSPK, Nidhhi Agerwal, and Bobby Deol, this foot-tapping track is composed by Oscar winner MM Keeravaani and directed by Jyothi Krisna & Krish Jagarlamudi.

Stay updated with the latest videos from Tips Telugu, Subscribe on the below link
https://youtube.com/TipsTelugu

Song Details : 
Song Name: Kollagottinadhiro
Music Director: M. M. Keeravaani 
Lyricist: Chandrabose 
Singers: Mangli, Rahul Sipligunj , Ramya Behara, Yamini Ghantasala. 
Chorus : Lokeshwar Edara, Sai Charan, Arun kaundinya, Airaa Udupi , Lipsika Bhashyam, Vaish
Programmed, Mixed and Mastered by : Jeevan Babu

Lyrics : 
Kora Kora Meesalatho, Kodama Kodama Adugulatho 
Kontey Kontey Chenukulatho, Kolimilanti Magatimitho Sarasara Vacchinaadu Chicchara Pidugantivaadu 
Edo Edo Thalachinaadu Evvarino Vethikinaadu 
Evaranta… Evaranta… Evarevaranta
Evaranta Evaranta Evarevarevarevaranta

Kondapalli Endi Bomma 
Kola Kallatho Chusindamma Teeyateeyani Teynelakomma
Teeyani Teraley Teesindamma
Vajrala Jilugulunna 
Rathnala Yelugulunna Kempulla Ompulunna Mohareela Merupulunna
Naa Paidi Gundeylona Edi Puttinchi 
Mariginchi Mariginchi Kariginchi Kariginchi

Kollagottinaadiro…..Kollagottinaadiro 
Kollagotti Naa Gundeyney Mulleygattinaadiro
Kollagottinaadiro…..Kollagottinaadiro 
Mulleygattinaadiro…Mulleygattinaadiro…

Ayyayyayyo….…Aa Chinnadi 
Inkemi Chesindayyo. 
Ayyayyayyo...Aa Kurradi Aa Mantram Esindayyo..

Kannulaloni Kaatuka Megham 
Seekati Naapai Silikindey 
Maatalathoney Melikeysindi 
Marmam Edo Daasindey
Aadavaallu Manasu Adavilantidani 
Eragani Santodiva
Antha Amayakudiva
Padusupilla Teeru Pattusikkadani Pasigattalenodiva 
Votti Shontikommuva…
Letha Ennapoosava…..
Are Meesala Roshala Monaganni Pattesi 
Pasivanni Chesesi Pasaredo Poosesi…
Kollagottinaadiro
Kollagotti Naa Gundeyney Mulleygattinaadiro 
Kollagottinaadiro….
Mulleygattinaadiro…Mulleygattinaadiro…

Oopiriloni Aaviripavanaaley 
Viriviga Lekhaley Visireney
Uppena Laaga Pongey Pourushamey 
Sogasuku Sankela Veseyney
Cheekuchintha Leni Vaadi Chittam Dochavey Parahushaar Poragadni Paagal Chesavey Daaredayina Davvedayina Needayi Untaney Pereydaina Teeredayina Penimiti Antaney Addeddedde….
Kollagottinaadiro….
Kollagotti Naa Gundeyney Mulleygattinaadiro 
Kollagottinaadiro Mulleygattinaadiro…

snippet.title: 'ഇളയമകൻ അഫ്സാന് ഒന്നും പറ്റിയിട്ടില്ലല്ലോ... എനിക്കൊന്ന് അവനെ കാണണമെന്നാ ഷെമി എന്നോട് പറഞ്ഞത്'
snippet.description:
'ഇളയമകൻ അഫ്സാന് ഒന്നും പറ്റിയിട്ടില്ലല്ലോ... എനിക്കൊന്ന് അവനെ കാണണമെന്നാ ഷെമി എന്നോട് പറഞ്ഞത്'; വെഞ്ഞാറമൂട് സംഭവത്തിൽ ​ഗുരുതരമായി പരിക്കേറ്റ ഉമ്മയെ ആശുപത്രിയിലെത്തി കണ്ടതിന് ശേഷം ബന്ധു.

MediaOne is a 24x7 news channel which broadcasts the updated news from trustworthy sources. The fastest-growing channel with varied presentations makes the channel unique. So stay tuned with MediaOne for the latest updates that are happening around the world.

കേരളത്തിലെ ഏറ്റവും മികച്ച വാര്‍ത്താ നെറ്റ്‌വര്‍ക്കാണ് മീഡിയവണ്‍. മൂല്യാധിഷ്ഠിതവും സ്വതന്ത്രവുമായ മാധ്യമപ്രവർത്തനം നടത്തുന്ന മലയാള ന്യൂസ് ടെലിവിഷൻ ചാനലാണിത്‌.  24 മണിക്കൂറും ലോകത്തിന്‍റെ ഏത് ഭാഗത്ത് നിന്നും ഇവിടെ തത്സമയം കാണാം. അതിവേഗം വാര്‍ത്താ വീഡിയോകള്‍ ലഭിക്കാൻ മീഡിയവണ്‍ സബ്സ്ക്രൈബ് ചെയ്യാം.

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 4329 - Bhide ke Jaal me Phase Mahagyani Baba?! | Taarak Mehta ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Bhide Bana Detactive | Bhide Ka Naya Mission | 

Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha

snippet.title: When You Have a Crush On Your Boss - Part 2| Ft. Keshav Sadhna,  Anjum Khan, Reshham Sahaani
snippet.description:
#filtercopy #officeromace #crush

Kaisa laga Part 2? Comments mein batao 😋

Ever felt that sudden wave of... something... when your boss is around? We're diving into that feeling! Yeah, we've all been there! In this super fun video, we're diving straight into the hilarious mess of having a crush on your boss! 😅

We've packed it with all the relatable moments of office romance, the kind where you're constantly wondering, "Is this real, or am I just imagining things?" 🤷‍♀️ From accidental touches during team meetings to trying to decipher those "friendly" smiles that might mean something more, every moment is a minefield of mixed signals.You know that feeling when you're trying to act cool, but your heart is doing a bhangra inside? 

This video is for anyone who's ever had a crush on their boss, found themselves overthinking every little interaction, or just loves a good dose of desi comedy. Get ready for some serious LOL moments, a few cringes (because, let's be honest, we've all been there!), and a whole lot of "OMG, same!" vibes.

So settle in, and get ready to dive into the chaos of office romance. Don't forget to LIKE, COMMENT, and SUBSCRIBE for more hilarious content! And share your own office crush stories in the comments – we want to hear all the juicy details! 😉 Let's see if your office crush stories are as crazy as ours!

Don't forget to follow us for more fun content!

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/filtercopy
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/FilterCopy/

en.title: When You Have a Crush On Your Boss - Part 2| Ft. Keshav Sadhna,  Anjum Khan, Reshham Sahaani
en.description:
#filtercopy #officeromace #crush

Kaisa laga Part 2? Comments mein batao 😋

Ever felt that sudden wave of... something... when your boss is around? We're diving into that feeling! Yeah, we've all been there! In this super fun video, we're diving straight into the hilarious mess of having a crush on your boss! 😅

We've packed it with all the relatable moments of office romance, the kind where you're constantly wondering, "Is this real, or am I just imagining things?" 🤷‍♀️ From accidental touches during team meetings to trying to decipher those "friendly" smiles that might mean something more, every moment is a minefield of mixed signals.You know that feeling when you're trying to act cool, but your heart is doing a bhangra inside? 

This video is for anyone who's ever had a crush on their boss, found themselves overthinking every little interaction, or just loves a good dose of desi comedy. Get ready for some serious LOL moments, a few cringes (because, let's be honest, we've all been there!), and a whole lot of "OMG, same!" vibes.

So settle in, and get ready to dive into the chaos of office romance. Don't forget to LIKE, COMMENT, and SUBSCRIBE for more hilarious content! And share your own office crush stories in the comments – we want to hear all the juicy details! 😉 Let's see if your office crush stories are as crazy as ours!

Don't forget to follow us for more fun content!

snippet.title: Saved In Drafts | Episode 1 - Second Chance | Mini Series | Take A Break Originals
snippet.description:
Episode 2 Out on 2nd March.
Amit and Darshana—two colleagues, two friends, and a bond that feels effortless. From shared coffee breaks to deep conversations, they understand each other in ways no one else does. But is it just friendship, or is there something more waiting to be realized? As they laugh, work, and navigate life together, one question lingers—where does this story lead? #SavedInDrafts begins.

snippet.title: Dupahiya Official Trailer | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents 
Dupahiya Official Trailer  
Starring Gajraj Rao, Sparsh Shrivastava, Renuka Shahane, Bhuvan Arora, Shivani Raghuvanshi, Yashpal Sharma, Komal Kushwaha 
Written by Chirag Garg, Avinash Dwivedi 
Directed by Sonam Nair 
Creators and Executive Producers - Salona Bains Joshi and Shubh Shivdasani
Production House - Bombay Film Cartel
 
Official Release Date Mar 7, 2025 on Prime Video India. 
 
About: 
Dhadakpur is the Belgium of Bihar. Clean, green and glorious. And this year the village will celebrate its Silver Jubilee of being crime- free! And as a gift for the villagers there will be a trophy, clean water but most of all pride. 
Also within 8 days, Roshni, the prettiest girl of the village will leave the Jha family and be wedded to Kuber. The plan was to marry his elder brother Durlabh, but the moment she heard that Durlabh’s younger brother works in Mumbai she didn’t even bat an eyelid to change the groom. Like her friends, Roshni too aspired for a modern city life.Her brother, Bhugol too has dreams of going to Mumbai and becoming a Bollywood superstar. 
 
The to-be-groom’s father is a clerk in the education department and Roshni’s dad, Banwari, is a temporary primary school teacher. This marriage meant his dream of a permanent job could be fulfilled. In short, everyone’s dreams hinge on this one wedding. But before their dreams could turn into reality, it was time to fulfill the to-be groom's dream. He wants a two-wheeler as a “wedding gift”. But not just any two-wheeler. A shiny red expensive motorbike! That too with a year’s supply of petrol. No one in Dhadakpur had paid such a handsome dowry before-but the Jha family is determined. 

The bike arrives in the day and disaster strikes at night. It got stolen! How? When? Who? There were only questions and no answers. Dhadakpur is crime-free after all! 
Leading the queue of suspects, was Roshni’s, ex-boyfriend, Amavas. Years ago, he was banished from Dhadakpur for his incessant stealing. 
Pushpalata Yadav, is Dhadakpur’s village head. It was her idea to banish Amavas from the village, but now he was their only hope. He could procure a second hand bike. 
Bhugol and Amavas are then sent to get the bike. Two childhood enemies. Chalk and cheese. Coffee and sleep. Ronaldo and The World Cup. How the two boys save the pride of the village and ensure the wedding happens as planned forms the crux of the season. 

ABOUT PRIME VIDEO
Prime Video is a one-stop entertainment destination offering customers a vast collection of premium programming in one application available across several devices. On Prime Video, customers can find their favourite Indian and international original series, movies, TV shows, and more, across multiple languages – including Indian-produced Original series like Mirzapur, Farzi, Panchayat, The Family Man, Dhootha, Jubilee, Dahaad, Made in Heaven, Suzhal – The Vortex, Inspector Rishi, Poacher, Indian Police Force, Paatal Lok, Rainbow Rishta, Wedding.con; Original movies like Maja Ma, Ammu, Mast Mein Rehne Ka; popular global Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Fallout, Reacher, The Boys, The Wheel of Time, Road House, The Idea of You; some of the biggest post-theatrical films; direct-to-service films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Bawaal, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, Pippa, HOME, Sharmajee Ki Beti, and many more of such titles. Additionally, Prime Video’s video entertainment marketplace, offers customers programming from partners such as Lionsgate Play, Discovery+ Crunchyroll, BBC Player, Sony Pictures – Stream, MGM+, FanCode, Chaupal, Manorama Max, Eros Now, Hoichoi, Anime Times, to name a few, via Prime Video add-on-subscriptions, as well as the option to rent movies, regardless of whether customers have a Prime membership or not. Customers can also go behind the scenes of their favorite movies and series with exclusive X-Ray access. Prime Video is one benefit among many that provides savings, convenience, and entertainment as part of the Prime membership. For more info visit www.amazon.com/primevideo.

snippet.title: Champions Trophy 2025 IND vs PAK: Pakistan की India के आगे हार, Pakistani Fan ने की भयंकर बेइज़्ज़ती
snippet.description:
Champions Trophy 2025 IND vs PAK: Pakistan की India के आगे हार, Pakistani Fan ने की भयंकर बेइज़्ज़ती 

#championstrophy2025 #indiavspakistan #indvspak   

आईसीसी चैंपियंस ट्रॉफी 2025 में भारत अपने सभी मुकाबले दुबई में खेलेगा जबकि पाकिस्तान बाकी देशों की मेजबानी करेगा. टूर्नामेंट का आगाज 19 फरवरी से हो चुका है और भारतीय टीम अपने अभियान की शुरुआत 20 फरवरी से कर चुकी है. बांग्लादेश के खिलाफ जीत के बाद पाकिस्तान के खिलाफ भी टीम इंडिया ने 6 विकेट से जीत हासिल की. इंडियन क्रिकेट फैंस में जहां ख़ुशी की लहर है, वहां पाकिस्तानी क्रिकेट फैंस को ये डर है कि पाकिस्तान चैंपियंस ट्रॉफी से लगभग बाहर हो चुकी है. भारत बनाम पाकिस्तान मैच के लिए कितने उत्सुक हैं पाकिस्तानी फैंस?भारत के लिए जीत के हीरो बने विराट कोहली जिन्होंने शानदार शतक ठोका. पाकिस्तान क्रिकेट टीम के फैंस इंडियन क्रिकेट टीम के क्यों हुए मुरीद? पाकिस्तानी टीम के स्टार खिलाड़ी बाबर आज़म, हारिस रउफ, शाहीन अफरीदी, मोहम्मद रिज़वान पर क्यों फूटा पाकिस्तान क्रिकेट फैंस का गुस्सा? बहुचर्चित पाकिस्तानी गेंदबाज़ी क्यों हुई शुबमन गिल, श्रेयस अय्यर, विराट, रोहित शर्मा के आगे फेल? क्या हुआ जब इंडिया बनाम पाकिस्तान मैच के बाद दुबई में इंडियन क्रिकेट फैंस और पाकिस्तान क्रिकेट फैंस ने मिलकर किया पाकिस्तान क्रिकेट टीम को ट्रोल और रोस्ट, जानने के लिए देखिये ज़ी स्विच की ये खास वीडियो. 

In the ICC Champions Trophy 2025, India will play all its matches in Dubai while Pakistan will host the rest of the countries. The tournament has started from February 19 and the Indian team has started its campaign from February 20. After the victory against Bangladesh, Team India also won against Pakistan by 6 wickets. While there is a wave of happiness among Indian cricket fans, Pakistani cricket fans are afraid that Pakistan is almost out of the Champions Trophy. How excited are Pakistani fans for the India vs Pakistan match? Virat Kohli became the hero of victory for India who scored a brilliant century. Why did the fans of the Pakistan cricket team become admirers of the Indian cricket team? Why did the Pakistan cricket fans get angry at the star players of the Pakistani team Babar Azam, Haris Rauf, Shaheen Afridi, Mohammad Rizwan? Why did the much-discussed Pakistani bowling fail in front of Shubman Gill, Shreyas Iyer, Virat, Rohit Sharma? What happened when after the India vs Pakistan match in Dubai, Indian cricket fans and Pakistani cricket fans together trolled and roasted the Pakistan cricket team. To know this, watch this special video of Zee Switch.

Mann Mast Malang Episode 03 - [Eng Sub] - Danish Taimoor - Sahar Hashmi - 23rd February 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Mann Mast Malang is a love story that traces the journey of two families who, once close and united by their children's engagement, become sworn enemies due to a single incident. As the story unfolds, Kabeer and Riya, former fiancés turned enemies, start to grow closer and eventually fall in love. Their love story faces the challenge of uniting their feuding families, as they strive to make their love successful against all odds.

snippet.description:
PANDLOYAMMA PALLU PART-2 FULL SONG | TELUGU FOLK SONG  | SUMAN BADANAKAL| RAMYASRI | PARSHURAM NAGAM

https://youtu.be/YBvXt1rlKdo

#PandloyammaPallu #PandloyammaPalluSong #PandloyammaPalluTeluguSong #PandloyammaPalluFolkSong #parshuramnagam #latestnewfolksongs #newfolksongs #telugufolksongs  

పండ్లోయమ్మ పండ్లు PART-1 
👇FULL SONG OUT NOW👇
https://youtu.be/NYgYbNgWasE

పాట నేపథ్యం:
అక్రమాసంబంధ0 పెట్టుకున్న.. ఓ ఇల్లాలును తన కొడుకు నిలదీయడంతో.. ప్రబుద్ధుడు చంపేస్తాడు. శవాన్ని పూడ్చే క్రమంలో ఎన్నెన్నో ఇబ్బందులు ఎదురౌతాయి. 
దాంతో.. ఇంట్లో.. కొడుకుని నిలువునా కోసి.. ఉప్పుకారం దట్టించి.. కూర వండుతుంది. అనుకోకుండా అప్పుడే.. భర్త రావడంతో... అదే కూరను.. భర్తకు వడ్డిస్తుంది. 
భర్త తింటావుంటే.. కంచంలో కొడుకు యొక్క వెండి ఉంగరం..  బంగారి గొలుసు కనబడుతుంది.
అంతే... మళ్ళీ ఆ ప్రబుద్ధుడు వచ్చి భర్తని కొట్టి సంపుతాడు. 
కానీ అదంతా గమనిస్తున్న దొంగలు.. ఇంటికి గడియవేసి.. నిప్పు పెడతారు.  దాంతో ఈ రంకు జంట కూడా బూడిద అయిపోతుంది. 

ఆ దొంగలు.. పక్కనే చెట్టుకింద.. బండకు ఉన్న కాళికా అమ్మవారిని మొక్కుతారు. 
కాళీమాత ప్రత్యక్షమై.. "జీగర్ల పుల్ల" (సంజీవని) ఇస్తుంది. దాంతో.. చనిపోయిన వాళ్ళందరిని.. ఈ దొంగలు ఎలా బతికించారో.. అద్భుతమైన విజువల్స్ తో చూసి.. SHARE  చేయండి. 

నీతి:  తాత్కాలిక ఆనందాల కోసం.. పాకులాడితే.. నా అనుకునే వాళ్లనే కాదు.. చివరికి తనకు తాను సర్వం కోల్పోతారు అని.. చాటి చెప్పే పాట ఇది.

మీ.. పరశురాం నాగం
(రైటర్ & డైరెక్టర్)


LYRICS & DIRECTOR : PARSHURAM NAGAM

TUNE: MANDA RAMU,

SINGERS: SUMAN BADANAKAL & MANDA SARASWATHI RAMU

MUSIC:  INDRAJITT 

DOP & EDITING, VFX: MOJESH KOLUGURI

CASTING:
RAMYA SRI MAMMU, RAJINI, KATHERAPAKA SRINIVAS, HARISH VELPULA, MANI, VEERA BHAI etc. 

PASTER: RANA

TECHNICAL SUPPORT : RAJASHEKHAR JAKKANI

ఈ పాటని నిర్మించినది: 
MANAIR PRODUCTION HOUSE, VEMULAWADA
మీకు Songs కావాలి అంటే: 9908233176 కి కాల్ చేయండి.

మా Instagram👇Message  చేయండి

https://www.instagram.com/manair_music_parshuram_nagam?igsh=MXhoYzNpNGtmemdtag==

నీతి:  తాత్కాలిక ఆనందాల కోసం.. పాకులాడితే.. నా అనుకునే వాళ్లనే కాదు.. చివరికి తనకు తాను సర్వం కోల్పోతారు అని.. చాటి చెప్పే పాట ఇది.

మీ.. పరశురాం నాగం
(రైటర్ & డైరెక్టర్)

snippet.title: Mann Mast Malang Episode 02 - [Eng Sub] - Danish Taimoor - Sahar Hashmi - 22nd February 2025
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Mann Mast Malang Episode 02 - [Eng Sub] - Danish Taimoor - Sahar Hashmi - 22nd February 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Mann Mast Malang is a love story that traces the journey of two families who, once close and united by their children's engagement, become sworn enemies due to a single incident. As the story unfolds, Kabeer and Riya, former fiancés turned enemies, start to grow closer and eventually fall in love. Their love story faces the challenge of uniting their feuding families, as they strive to make their love successful against all odds.

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Ali Faizan
Writer: Nooran Makhdoom

Cast:
Danish Taimoor as Kabir 
Sahar Hashmi as Riya 
Saba Hamid as Mah Bina 
Uzma Hassan as Asma 
Adnan Samad as Sikandar 
Hiba Ali Khan as Wafa 
Nayyer Ejaz as Chacha 
Dodi Khan as Wajid 
Ramiz Siddiqui as Rameez 
Yasir Alam as Yasir 
Kamran Jeelani as Mubeen
Sheherzade Noor Peerzada as Kashaf 
Maha Hasan as Minha  
Faisal Bali as Bhola 
Sharif Baloch as Inspector
Harmain Ghalib as Kabir (young) 
Aayat Arif as Riya (young)
